modName: Dragon Shouts - FALCON PUNCH and FALCON KICK
summary: Replaces the Fus Roh Dah and Wuld Nah Kest audio... with Captain Falcon.
descriptionHtml:
Replaces the Fus Roh & Fus Roh Dah audio with Captain Falcons\' classic Falcon Punch for Males of all races.
Replaces the Wuld, Wuld Nah, and Wuld Nah Kest audio with Captain Falcons\' classic Falcon Kick. (Thanks JimmyFrost :D)
And Finally, replaces the one word \"Fus\" with Captain Falcons\' classic \"YES!\"
Any suggestions/improvements are appreciated :) 

HOW TO INSTALL
Extract to Skyrim/data/

HOW TO UNINSTALL
Delete the files starting with voicepowers_shout from the MaleArgonian, MaleElfHaughty, MaleEvenToned, MaleKhajiit, and MaleOrc folders.
author: Evilnms

files.name: Skyrim Falcon PunchKickYes
